2. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper uses semantic image segmentation as the meta representation for relating the perception and control policy modules. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning agent for the control policy module. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses machine learning techniques for training robots in virtual environments. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the use of simulators for training robots and proposes a modular architecture for virtual-to-real transfer learning, which involves control policy modules.
